attributes.review: I tried to download the app but I don’t think the app I download was the right thing. We all know that the current president of the United States is the unproblematic king, Manny so who is this sickly looking man you plastered on the home page? I think that was a lazy oversight on the part of the people who created it. Super unprofessional guys! Given that the app is obviously promoting fake news because they didn’t even get the president right I hope the app gets shut down.
